  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Growth Trainee",
  "description": "<h2>🚀 Sales Growth Trainee</h2><p>✨ Like meeting people, staying active, and learning skills you can actually use?</p><p>At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, you’ll be part of on-ground campaigns, events, and roadshows where brands meet people face-to-face. This role is all about building confidence, communication, and real-world sales experience through hands-on learning.</p><h2>💼 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><ul><li><p>👋 Engage the public at roadshows, pop-ups, and event booths</p></li><li><p>📣 Represent client brands in a professional and positive way</p></li><li><p>💬 Create friendly, meaningful conversations with customers</p></li><li><p>🤝 Work with your team to support events and achieve campaign goals</p></li></ul><h2>🎯 What You’ll Get</h2><ul><li><p>🎓 Full training provided — no experience needed</p></li><li><p>📈 Performance-based growth with clear progression opportunities</p></li><li><p>🌍 Exposure to different events and campaigns</p></li><li><p>🤝 Supportive coaching, mentorship, and a collaborative team</p></li></ul><h2>🙌 This Role Is Great For You If You</h2><ul><li><p>Enjoy talking to people and meeting new faces</p></li><li><p>Are open to learning and receiving feedback</p></li><li><p>Are reliable, positive, and team-oriented</p></li><li><p>Prefer active, on-the-ground work over desk-based roles</p></li></ul><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>If you’re keen to gain hands-on experience in events, public engagement, and sales, we’d love to connect.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
